175 A.3d 176 VERONICA CARTER, PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. JOSEPH POPOVICH, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-360 September Term 2017

079653 November 29, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001072-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
